                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Quito</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-04-01"><hi rend="italic">April 1,
